divs: sighting detailson vacation in santa fe, nm. my wife and i were on the balcony of our hotel taking pictures of each other. i thought it would be funny to snap some pics of the night sky because i had been joking about area 51 with my wife. i took 11 pics about 2 seconds apart and in about the same area. when i looked at the back of the lcd display to review, i saw that some of the pics had white dots in them and showed my wife. she laughed and we forgot about them. i recently looked at them and zoomed in on these dots. they look like donut shaped gases. in one of them it looks like something is entering\exiting it. it's pretty strange. i will include the original and the cropped pics. you need to zoom in close to see the detail.
